Label: util_TNC Single - Cost
Expression: @((np.maximum(TNC_single_baseFare + df.s2_dist_skims * TNC_single_costPerMile + df.s2_time_skims * TNC_single_costPerMinute, TNC_single_costMinimum) * 100 + df.s2_cost_skims)) / (np.maximum(df.income,1000)**df.income_exponent)

Label: util_TNC Shared_switch
Description: TNC Shared - switch turn-off (depends on data availability)

Label: util_TNC Shared - In-vehicle time
Expression: @(np.where(df.nev_available, df.nev_time, np.where(df.microtransit_available, df.microtransit_time, df.s3_time_skims))) * TNC_shared_IVTFactor * df.time_factor

Label: util_TNC Shared - Cost
Expression: @np.where(df.nev_available, nevCost, np.where(df.microtransit_available, microtransitCost, (np.maximum(TNC_shared_baseFare + df.s3_dist_skims * TNC_shared_costPerMile + df.s3_time_skims * TNC_shared_costPerMinute, TNC_shared_costMinimum) * 100 + df.s3_cost_skims))) / (np.maximum(df.income,1000)**df.income_exponent)
